The '''Horn Estate''' was the mansion that [[Rostek Horn]] lived in, near [[Coronet City/Legends|Coronet City]] on [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]]. It was built by the [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] government after they burned his old house down in [[7 ABY/Legends|7 ABY]], in an unsuccessful attempt to destroy the old [[Corellian Security Force|CorSec]] files he had.

